	Sneakyjoystick
	- A joystick for use with iPhone Game Development
	- Independent of external libraries
  	- This project is generally updated to work with the latest trunk 
  		of Cocos2d-iPhone
  	- Special thanks to @tanis2000, who ported the code to work with 
  		Cocos2D iPhone v3 (develop-v3 branch)
  	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 NEED IMPLEMENTATION HELP? I will help you for free, if you do not speak English
 I will get a hold of a translater and we ca work it out :) 

 If you have implementation issues, PLEASE do not file issues, those are for actual issues with the code, not your issue implementing this input framework. Email me instead and I promise I will help. 
